with  the  NextGen.  If  we  can  accelerate  them  and  put  the  system 
in place earlier for all those who fly, it maximizes the benefits. But 
we  all  know,  none  of  us  pay  for  major  capital  investments  on  a 
cash-and-carry  basis,  which  is  what  we’ve  been  attempting  to  do. 
The  potential  that  we  can,  if  needed,  use  that  kind  of  authority, 
again,  goes  back  to  a  fee-based  system.  That’s  what  enables  that. 
So, I would recommend looking at some of the mechanics that we 
have  there,  as  well  as  the  fact  we  believe  it  makes  sense  to  have 
